commentary: Mashrafe Mortaza to Taylor, OUT and a nightmare start! Fuller ball outside the off stump. Taylor opens his arms and drives it to extra-cover. Shuvo moves to his left and fields. He sees that Taylor is half-way down the pitch and throws it to the keeper's end. Rahim need not even lay a finger on it as the throw takes the bails off. Run-out of a free-hit!

commentary: Price to Shakib Al Hasan, OUT good length ball on the middle stump. Shakib comes down the track and slogs it straight down the throat of Taylor at long-on. A needless shot at this time as victory is in sight! It is at these times that Zimbabwe will wonder what would have happened had they got Tamim earlier
